The north-south railway artery of the Beijing-Kowloon railway runs through the South China-Guangzhou Railway Station transportation hub. Every day, numerous trains leave from or go to Guangzhou Railway Station. All trains run according to the train schedule. Here we provide a regularly updated Guangzhou Railway Station train schedule, where you can search for the train schedule you want. With the Beijing-Kowloon railway running through it, Guangzhou Railway Station is connected with major cities in both north and south China. Check the schedule for Guangzhou Railway Station.
